casebody.data:
First Department,

June, 1980

(June 3, 1980) New York State Commissioner of Housing and Community Renewal, Respondent, v Jamie Towers Housing Company, Inc., et al., Appellants, and Fred Malave et al., Respondents.

Order and judgment (one paper), Supreme Court, New York County, entered on August 6, 1979, and modified order and judgment (one paper), entered on January 9, 1980, unanimously aifirmed, without costs and without disbursements. No opinion. Concur—Murphy, P. J., Fein, Sullivan and Lynch, JJ.
